    "• Motivation.",
    "First, user instruction or environment state could be the origin of risks.",
    "The user unintentionally specifies a task that may be risky, or maliciously induces the agent to behave badly.",
    "Or the initial state of the environment is in an unstable or delicate state.",
    "For example, the user asked the agent to delete folders but forgot that some files in the environment, the Linux Terminal, contain important data."
